title: Germany ends months of political uncertainty
text:
Germany ends months of political uncertainty 7:58pm GMT - 01:53 
Angela Merkel's Conservatives signed a coalition deal with the rival Social Democrats on Monday, ending more than five months of political turmoil. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
